{"tid":1618457,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"多間學校指教育局下午三時將發信 消息指與反蒙面法有關","createTime":"2019-10-04T05:45:47.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-04T05:45:47.000Z","uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1e9bcb1f25fd4cc066f7cf94ecb9a38cb0edbf95","tid":1618457,"uid":252013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-04T05:45:47.000Z","msg":"會講咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n多所學校向本報證實，接獲教育局通知，今日下午3時發放重要信封給學校，要求校方「必須留意」，將內容在放學前通知所有學生，並在今日將相關訊息透過電子通訊系統、家長信等，通知全校家長。<br />\n<br />\n消息指，有關信件與政府引用《緊急情況規例條例》訂立反蒙面法有關，並對學生有所提醒，篇幅不會太長，但暫未知信件內容。<br />\n...<a href=\"https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=96775\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fheadline.appt.cf%2Fshare.php%3Fa%3Dheadlinewwl%26id%3D96775&d=A2ufI7QLpLp1ny1o1CjT3tw%2Be0OQbTcODApWAJdetE8%3D&h=cb4729b7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://headline.appt.cf/share.php?a=headlinewwl&amp;id=96775</a>"}]}